2. Then, I need to determine the cost of goods sold from these sales
3. Finally, subtract COGS from sales revenue to get gross profit

- "amount" which represents the sale amount
- "cost_amount" which represents the cost of the products sold
- "profit" which is already calculated as the difference between sales and cost
